# Optional allow-list for r10k environments (one name per line).
# If this file is installed as /opt/openvox-gui/etc/allowed-environments.txt
# (or OPENVOX_GUI_ALLOWED_ENVS_FILE points at a copy), scripts/r10k-deploy.sh
# will reject any first positional argument not listed here.
#
# Leave the installed file absent to allow any environment name that passes
# the shape validation (legacy behaviour). Populate from your control-repo
# branches / r10k sources for stricter production posture (srsysarch1 #8).
#
# Examples:
# production
# development
# staging
# feature/my-branch
